1\264\347\232\204\347\251\272\346\260\224\350\264\250\351\207\217\346\230\216\346\230\276"
    20: "\346\234\211\344\270\212\345\215\207\350\266\213\345\212\277."
    20: "people\'s lives and properties.Taking Shenyang weather as an example,the day-by-day weather data from 2012 to 2023 is used for data processing and visualization analysis of weather based on <span class=\'highlight\'>python</span>.According "
    20: "In the field of meteorology,by utilizing advanced data processing and graphic display technologies,complex meteorological data are transformed into intuitive and easy-to-understand graphics and "
