    20: "\344\275\234\347\224\250,\345\234\250\344\270\200\345\256\232\347\250\213\345\272\246\344\270\212\350\247\243\345\206\263\344\272\206\346\225\260\346\215\256\344\274\240\350\276\223\345\273\266\350\277\237\351\227\256\351\242\230.\345\220\214\346\227\266,\345\234\250\350\276\205\345\212\251\346\211\247\346\263\225\346\226\271\351\235\242\344\271\237\350\265\267\345\210\260\344\272\206\351\242\204\350\255\246\346\225\210\346\236\234.\346\234\254\346\226\207\344\273\213\347\273\215\344\272\206\350\257\245\347\263\273\347\273\237\345\273\272\350\256\276\347\232\204\350\203\214\346\231\257\343\200\201\350\256\276\350\256\241\346\200\235\350\267\257\343\200\201\347\263\273\347\273\237\346\241\206\346\236\266,\344\273\245\345\217\212\345\205\266\345\234\250\350\276\205\345\212\251\346\211\247\346\263\225\346\226\271\351\235\242\347\232\204\346\211\251\345\261\225\345\272\224\347\224\250,\344\273\205\344\276\233\345\220\214\350\241\214\345\217\202\350\200\203."
    20: "developed based on <span class=\'highlight\'>Python</span> web scraper technology,and successfully played the role of early warning for many times with good effect,solving the delayed data transmission to a certain extent,and also assisting "
    20: "In 2016,quarantine data interchange with National Animal Quarantine Big Data Platform(NAQBDP)was completed by Henan Animal Quarantine E-certification Platform(HAQEP).The quarantine data collected by "
    20: "the NAQBDP had been used as a final judge reference when vehicles transporting livestock and poultry were inspected since the designated pathway system was implemented,however,the inspection in the "
    20: "designated pathway would be seriously affected if the data transmission between the two platforms delayed.In order to timely find out such delay,an animal quarantine information early warning system was "
    20: "law enforcement as an early warning tool.Here,the background under which the system was constructed,design idea,system framework and its extended application in auxiliary law enforcement were introduced"
